item.title: Whats Up
item.description: I’ve always thought on writting stuff on the WWW, but I never got full hands to it, until now, so I would like to welcome you to what intends to be my new blog/site where you can find all about the things that I’m most interested in, you can expect to find stuff such as: Music (mostly punk) Programming (Python, Javascript, Swift and bit of everything) WWII Podcast RPG games Before digging into different topics I would like introduce myself.
